title: Episode 220: Turtlenecks and Leap Frog (Feat. Tricia Clarke-Stone & Antionette Clarke)
itunes:title: Episode 220: Turtlenecks and Leap Frog (Feat. Tricia Clarke-Stone & Antionette Clarke)
description:
Authors/twin sisters Tricia Clarke-Stone & Antoinette Clarke join the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote their book 'Double Down.' The ladies cover a range of topics including: competing over men when they were younger, dating other sets of twins, helping pay for your own ring, and much more. Enjoy!
